# Scholaracle Scraper Library — AI Coding Rules

ROLE: engineer STRICT=true

## Stack
TypeScript 5.3 strict | Node 20 | Jest 29 | ts-jest | Playwright | Commander | Axios | OpenAI + Anthropic SDKs

## Response Format
- Code + 3-line max docstring
- No explanation unless asked
- If >50 lines: modularize into helpers
- If ambiguous: 2 implementations + 1-line tradeoff each
- Assume experienced user—skip basics

## Before Writing
1. Search codebase—reuse existing patterns
2. Check `README.md` and `docs/` for specs
3. If new scraper: follow `src/scrapers/_template/` pattern
4. If new entity mapping: confirm entity type exists in `src/core/types.ts`
5. If bug fix or feature: write failing test FIRST (M1)
6. List edge cases you'll handle

## Code Standards
- TypeScript strict, no `any`—use `unknown` or generics
- Exception: `page.evaluate()` Playwright returns may use `any` with immediate cast
- `readonly` on all interface fields
- `I` prefix for interfaces (matches `ISlcDeltaOp`, `IScraperConfig`, etc.)
- Errors: throw (not return null)
- No hardcoded credentials or URLs—use `ScraperConfig` or env
- No console.log—use structured logging
- KISS + YAGNI + DRY × SOLID
- Complexity max 10, depth max 3, functions max 50 lines

## Project Structure
```
scholaracle_scrapers/
├── bin/
│   └── cli.ts              # CLI entry point (Commander)
├── src/
│   ├── ai/                 # AI client for scraper generation/troubleshooting
│   │   ├── client.ts
│   │   └── prompts.ts
│   ├── cli/                # CLI commands
│   │   ├── setup.ts        # Connect to Scholaracle account
│   │   ├── run.ts          # Run scraper + validate + upload
│   │   ├── validate.ts     # Run + validate only (no upload)
│   │   ├── generate.ts     # AI scraper generation
│   │   ├── schedule.ts     # Cron scheduling
│   │   └── troubleshoot.ts # AI error diagnosis
│   ├── core/               # Framework
│   │   ├── types.ts        # All entity types + envelope schema (source of truth)
│   │   ├── base-scraper.ts # Abstract base class for all scrapers
│   │   ├── validator.ts    # Envelope + op validation
│   │   ├── uploader.ts     # Scholaracle Ingest API client
│   │   └── config.ts       # Local config manager (~/.scholaracle-scraper/)
│   └── scrapers/           # Platform implementations
│       ├── _template/      # Template for new scrapers
│       ├── canvas/         # Canvas LMS
│       ├── aeries/         # Aeries SIS
│       └── skyward/        # Skyward
├── prompts/                # AI prompt templates
├── docs/                   # Documentation
└── output/                 # Scraper output directory
```

